here is a list of what we did:

- crab some coffee in the morning 
- walked to the best bakery mamiche & had some fresh bread & cinnamon rolls 
- walked through the streets of paris 
- had the famous hot chocolate at café carette 
- dinner at monsieu bleu 
- watched the eiffel tower by night at place du trocadéro
